{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She is surprised to see him.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAAVIK
{META_DATA}: (continuing)
{DIALOGUE}: Thank you, sir.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kirk nods, the doors close.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: There is an uneasy forced intimacy between them.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Lieutenant, are you wearing your hair differently?
