{DIALOGUE}: I failed to resolve the situation.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: There is no correct resolution.
{DIALOGUE}: It is a test of character.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAAVIK
{DIALOGUE}: May I ask how you dealt with the test?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{META_DATA}: (amused)
{DIALOGUE}: You may ask, Lieutenant.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She stares.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{META_DATA}: (continuing)
{DIALOGUE}: That was a little joke.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAAVIK
{DIALOGUE}: Humor... that is a difficult concept ... it is not logical...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: We learn by doing, Lieutenant.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She's a laugh a minute.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kirk pushes the button; the elevator starts.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{META_DATA}: (continuing)
{DIALOGUE}: You want my advice?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She studies him, considering.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: No doubt about it, the attraction is mutual and she has no idea how to handle it.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAAVIK
{DIALOGUE}: Yes.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Take the test again.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The lift stops and the doors open.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BONES
