{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He reacts to them.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Saavik exits demurely.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAAVIK
{DIALOGUE}: Thank you, sir.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Bones enters and the doors close.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kirk studies the ceiling.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BONES
{DIALOGUE}: Has she changed her hairstyle?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kirk says nothing.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BONES
{META_DATA}: (finally)
{DIALOGUE}: Wonderful stuff, that Romulan ale --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: UHURA'S VOICE
{DIALOGUE}: Admiral Kirk --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Kirk here.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: UHURA'S VOICE
{DIALOGUE}: I have an urgent CommPic from Space Lab Regula I for the Admiral.
{DIALOGUE}: Dr. Carol Marcus.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: In my quarters, Uhura.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: UHURA'S VOICE
{DIALOGUE}: Yes, sir.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Awkward silence.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BONES
{DIALOGUE}: It never rains but when it pours --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: As a physician you of all people should appreciate the danger of re-opening old wounds.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The elevator stops.
