{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The doors close.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BONES
{META_DATA}: (annoyed with himself)
{DIALOGUE}: Sorry.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 53 INT. KIRK'S QUARTERS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Featuring VIEW SCREEN: A scramble of interference and noise.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A piece of Carol's VOICE breaks through now and again as we PULL BACK revealing a frustrated Kirk.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Uhura.
{DIALOGUE}: Can't you augment?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: UHURA
{DIALOGUE}: I'm trying, sir.
{DIALOGUE}: Stand by...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Carol's face appears.
