{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Raise shields!
{DIALOGUE}: Energize phasers, stand by to --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: But the ENTIRE BRIDGE is ROCKED by a shock impact, some of the crew sent flying.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 76 EXT.SPACE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reliant firing phasers at Enterprise.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A hit in the rear of the engine room area, debris flying into the void.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 77 INT. ENTERPRISE ENGINE ROOM
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: An explosion rips through the facility, sending yellow- ish green GAS hurtling down the long facility towards us.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Crewmen are hurled through the air, screaming.
{META_DATA}: 78 ANGLE - THE GREAT AUTO DOORS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: roll closed, sealing off the damaged tail section, SIRENS SHRIEKING!
{META_DATA}: 79 ANGLE - THE TRAINEES
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: terrified, scramble to get out amid the deadly yellow- ish green smoke, the cries.
