{META_DATA}: 81 HIGH ANGLE - ENGINE ROOM
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The angle we saw during inspection.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The trainees, in panic amid the gas crawl over each other trying to get out.
