{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: On screen.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: UHURA
{META_DATA}: (hesitating)
{DIALOGUE}: Admiral --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Do it, while we have time.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: All eyes go to the SCREEN.
