{CHARACTER_NAME}: KHAN
{DIALOGUE}: I give you sixty seconds, Admiral.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kirk turns from the screen --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SPOCK
{DIALOGUE}: Admiral, you can't give him Genesis...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: At least we know he hasn't got it.
{DIALOGUE}: Just keep nodding as though I'm giving orders.
