{DIALOGUE}: Khan, how do I know you'll keep your word?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KHAN
{META_DATA}: (on screen)
{DIALOGUE}: I've given you no word to keep, Admiral.
{DIALOGUE}: In my judgment, you simply have no alternative.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: I take your point.
{DIALOGUE}: Stand by to receive our transmission.
