{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Khan sighs, contentedly.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KHAN
{DIALOGUE}: Excellent.
{DIALOGUE}: We have all the time in the world.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 146 INT. ROCKY CAVERN
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As before, Saavik is on the communicator.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAAVIK
