{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 150 EXT. SPACE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Dark side of Gamma.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reliant sits idle.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 150A INT. ROCKY CAVERN
