{META_DATA}: 150E FULL SHOT - THE GENESIS CAVE (MATTE AND FX) (FORMERLY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SCENE 130)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A huge cavern.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kirk is actually standing at the middle of it.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Space extends vastly above and below his point of view.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Like Eden, lush growth everywhere, water- falls, and a cobalt blue sky high, high above where a round orb glows sending light and warmth downward.
