{DIALOGUE}: Remind me to explain to you the concept of human ego.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Best speed, Scotty...
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 169 EXT. SPACE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Enterprise whooshes by CAMERA leaving Regula behind.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reliant now appears in far b.g. and CAMERA BEGINS A MOVE to her.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 170 INT. RELIANT BRIDGE
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KHAN
{DIALOGUE}: There!
{DIALOGUE}: Full impulse power!
{DIALOGUE}: Not so wounded as we were led to believe -- so much the better...
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 171 EXT. SPACE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reliant moves to and past CAMERA in hot pursuit.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 172 EXT. SPACE - SERIES OF SHOTS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Call them SPACE-BYS.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Enterprise rushes TOWARD US, flashes BY and CONTINUES towards the swirling nebula.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: THEN Reliant does the same, closer in pursuit.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: At this moment, half the distance between Regula and the nebula has been covered.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 173 INT. ENTERPRISE BRIDGE
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SPOCK
{DIALOGUE}: Estimating nebula penetration in two minutes.
{DIALOGUE}: Reliant is closing.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Steady as you go...
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 174 EXT. SPACE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Orientation, SHOT.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reliant can clearly see where Enterprise is headed --
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 175 INT. RELIANT BRIDGE
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JOACHIM
{DIALOGUE}: We'll lose them if they go in there.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KHAN
{DIALOGUE}: Rake her.
{META_DATA}: 176 SOMEONE PUNCHES A BUTTON
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 177 EXT. SPACE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reliant's shot crosses Enterprise's bow --
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 178 INT. ENTERPRISE HOSPITAL
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The ship reverberates with the near miss.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Chekov wakes up, looks wildly about --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BONES
{DIALOGUE}: Take it easy --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CHEKOV
{DIALOGUE}: But I must --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BONES
{DIALOGUE}: Listen to me, Pavel; you haven't the strength or the equilibrium --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CHEKOV
{DIALOGUE}: But --
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As they talk, David, unnoticed, leaves the area.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Enterprise is buffeted again --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: CAROL
{DIALOGUE}: Dr. McCoy, I can't just sit here.
{DIALOGUE}: Tell me what I can do.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BONES
{META_DATA}: (grim)
{DIALOGUE}: You can help get my surgery squared away.
{DIALOGUE}: I'm expecting customers.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She whitens in fear.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANOTHER SHOT reverberates.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 179 INT. ENTERPRISE BRIDGE
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAAVIK
{DIALOGUE}: That was close --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{META_DATA}: (unfazed)
{DIALOGUE}: They just don't want us going in there.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SPOCK
{DIALOGUE}: One minute to nebula perimeter.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The bridge door slides open and David enters.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He stares in wonder.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Saavik reacts to David.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SPOCK
{META_DATA}: (continuing)
{DIALOGUE}: Admiral, they're reducing speed.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Uhura, patch me in --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: UHURA
{DIALOGUE}: Aye, sir.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 180 INT. RELIANT BRIDGE
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KHAN
{DIALOGUE}: Why are we slowing?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JOACHIM
{DIALOGUE}: We daren't follow them into the nebula, sir -- our shields will be useless...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK'S VOICE
{DIALOGUE}: This is Admiral Kirk.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Khan's eyes bulge --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK'S VOICE
{META_DATA}: (continuing)
{DIALOGUE}: We tried it once your way, Khan.
{DIALOGUE}: Are you game for a rematch?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Khan's eyes bulge --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK'S VOICE
{META_DATA}: (continuing)
{DIALOGUE}: Khan -- !
{DIALOGUE}: I'm laughing at the "superior" intellect.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KHAN
{DIALOGUE}: Full impulse power!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JOACHIM
{DIALOGUE}: No sir!
{DIALOGUE}: We have Genesis -- Whatever you want --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KHAN
{DIALOGUE}: Full power damn you!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And he reaches across and executes it himself.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 181 INT. ENTERPRISE BRIDGE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They react to Reliant's speed-up.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The nebula approach is ON SCREEN.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{META_DATA}: (dry)
{DIALOGUE}: I'll say this for him: he's consistent.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 182 EXT. SPACE - THE MUTARA NEBULA
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WE'RE VERY CLOSE NOW, and SEE CLEARLY the swirling, slowly moving gases, magenta, purple, etc.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: There are veils of luminescent materials and through all an interlace of unpredictable electrical charges.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Like lightning, these intermittent great flashes illumine whole sections of the nebula.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: OUR VIEW is moving slowly forward...
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 183 INT. ENTERPRISE BRIDGE
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SPOCK
{META_DATA}: (timing)
{DIALOGUE}: And we're... in.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 184 EXT. SPACE - THE NEBULA
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As Enterprise whooshes into the PICTURE headed into the purplish gas -- and disappears into a cloud bank of the stuff.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A moment then Reliant APPEARS, pursues Enterprise into the gloom, also disappears.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 185 INT. RELIANT BRIDGE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ON SCREEN the picture is squirrelly purple, breaking up.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Blindness.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Panic.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KHAN
{DIALOGUE}: Tactical!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JOACHIM
{META_DATA}: (tries)
{DIALOGUE}: Inoperative.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KHAN
{DIALOGUE}: Raise the shields...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Electrical forces raging without are also reflected on the circuits within.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It's bumpy, on top of everything else.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Electronic WHINING.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JOACHIM
{DIALOGUE}: As I feared, sir.
{DIALOGUE}: Not functional.
{DIALOGUE}: I'm reducing speed.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Khan does not argue.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 186 EXT. SPACE - PURPLE - SERIES OF SHOTS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Cautiously Reliant emerges from a massive "cloudbank."
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Electrical discharges abound.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Barely moving, she feels her way forward.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Alone.
{META_DATA}: 187 AS THE ANGLE WIDENS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A treat: Enterprise is above and behind Reliant.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 188 INT. ENTERPRISE BRIDGE - ON SCREEN
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reliant's image is breaking up.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SULU
{DIALOGUE}: Phaser lock inoperative, sir.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Best guess, Mr. Sulu.
{DIALOGUE}: Fire when ready.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Sulu strains, then fires -- just as an electrical dis- turbance bounces the bridge --
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 189 EXT. SPACE NEBULA
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The bounce causes Sulu's phaser shot to go wide of Reliant, amid CRACKLING discharges --
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 190 INT. RELIANT BRIDGE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Rolls from the near-miss concussion --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KHAN
{DIALOGUE}: Aft-torpedoes -- fire -- !
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 191 EXT. SPACE NEBULA
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reliant is wide of the mark with a Photon torpedo.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A BLINDING ELECTRICAL DISCHARGE.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: When it clears, Enterprise appears to be alone.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 192 INT. ENTERPRISE BRIDGE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ON SCREEN, nothing but magenta amid picture breakup --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{META_DATA}: (sweating)
{DIALOGUE}: Hold your course.
{DIALOGUE}: Look sharp...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAAVIK
{DIALOGUE}: At what.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 193 EXT. NEBULA (INTERCUT WITH BRIDGE)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Enterprise feeling its way...
{META_DATA}: 194 ON BRIDGE - POV ON SCREEN
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: All peer into the lousy picture.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Occasional electrical flashes.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 195 EXT. SPACE NEBULA
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Still Enterprise moves forward... A LARGE FLASH... a SUDDEN GLIMPSE: Reliant boring in on collision course!
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 196 INT. ENTERPRSIE BRIDGE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A sudden clearing ON SCREEN: Reliant!
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Evasive starboard!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hard over, but not fast enough.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reliant fires a phaser.
{META_DATA}: 197 SERIES OF SHOTS
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reliant's phaser shot hits the Enterprise torpedo room in Dorsal Fin area of ship.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 198 INT. ENTERPRISE TORPEDO ROOM
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: An EXPLOSION rocks the room and...
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 199 INT. ENTERPRISE BRIDGE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Bridge rattles from the explosion below; Sulu is thrown from his chair.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Saavik leaps to her post --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Phaser bank one, fire!
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 200 EXT. SPACE NEBULA
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Enterprise fires a phaser and delivers a raking shot -- which rips along the side of Reliant's primary hull.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 200A INT. RELIANT BRIDGE (FORMERLY SCENE 205)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The bridge is damaged; Joachim and others are wounded...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KHAN
{DIALOGUE}: Joachim!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: For the first time, his friend wounded, Khan hesitates, holds him --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: JOACHIM
{DIALOGUE}: Yours... is... the superior...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KHAN
{DIALOGUE}: I shall avenge you --
{META_DATA}: 200B NEW ANGLE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: She veers to one side with the impact and disappears into a deep purple mass.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 201 INT. ENTERPRISE BRIDGE
