{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Damage, Scotty?
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 202 INT. ENGINE ROOM
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Bones is there, helping some crewmen.
