{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The air is heavy with smoke but the doors, damaged earlier, still hold.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SCOTTY
{DIALOGUE}: Admiral, I've got to take the mains off the line.
{DIALOGUE}: The energizer's shaken loose and I can't get in there to fix her -- radiation --
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 203 INT. ENTERPRISE BRIDGE
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: All right, we'll do the job with auxiliary power.
