{CHARACTER_NAME}: CHEKOV
{DIALOGUE}: Could you use another hand, Admiral?
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Man the weapons console, Mr. Chekov.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: ANGLE FAVORING David as the others react to Chekov taking his place.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Quiet.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{META_DATA}: (continuing)
{DIALOGUE}: Spock?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Spock is bent over the scanner --
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SPOCK
