{DIALOGUE}: His pattern indicates two dimensional thinking...
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Kirk looks at him, smiles.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Mr. Saavik, all stop.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAAVIK
{DIALOGUE}: All stop, sir.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Descend ten thousand meters.
{DIALOGUE}: Stand by photon torpedoes.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 204 EXT. SPACE NEBULA
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reliant in purplish mass, banking slightly, completing a long turn, then boring ahead.
{META_DATA}: 205 OMITTED
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 206 EXT. SPACE NEBULA
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: As Reliant emerges from the dark blue mass into a clear almost tranquil place.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reliant, moving slowly, stops, as if looking around.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 207 INT. RELIANT BRIDGE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The screens are empty.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KHAN
{DIALOGUE}: Where is he?
{DIALOGUE}: Where in God's name is he?
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 208 EXT. SPACE NEBULA
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reliant motionless in the f.g. amid occasional flashes.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Now, behind Reliant and from below, like a great whale rising from the depths, Enterprise rises vertically, slowly passing the unsuspecting enemy.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: When Enterprise is above, behind and quite close:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 209 INT. ENTERPRISE BRIDGE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reliant ON SCREEN, intermittent but clear.
