{DIALOGUE}: Torpedoes ready, sir.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Fire.
{META_DATA}: 210 SERIES OF SHOTS
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: A) EXT. ENTERPRISE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: fires torpedo; one which hits, destroying Reliant's weapons pod on top.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: B) INT. RELIANT
