{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: D) EXT. ENTERPRISE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: fires two more times.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The first causes general damage.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The second, close behind blasts Reliant's port engine off into space, debris scattering.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: E) INT. RELIANT BRIDGE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: is devastated.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Khan is blown from his chair and WE'RE UNCERTAIN of his fate.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 211 EXT. SPACE NEBULA
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Reliant, now a scarred, battered hulk, her main hull still intact, but dead in space.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 212 INT. ENTERPRISE BRIDGE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: No cheers, just deadly professionalism.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
{DIALOGUE}: Cease fire.
{DIALOGUE}: Look sharp.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAAVIK
{DIALOGUE}: Power levels quite low, sir.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: KIRK
