{CHARACTER_NAME}: UHURA
{DIALOGUE}: Aye, sir.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: 213 INT. RELIANT BRIDGE
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Amid the smoke and ruins, WE SEE no signs of life.
